Open Interview1 MVC solution from Github.

Write some code to open the file called 'Juxtapositions'. The file is in the Git Repo.

Each line is a database record. Each column of the record is delimited with the '|' character.
 
Create a List containing each record, then sort through the list and find all records containing the word 'juxtaposition'.

Print the List of records containing the word juxtaposition on the console and save it to a new file in the solution folder. Print out the count also.